            <h1>BOURBON CHICKEN</h1>
            <p class="lead">PREP TIME: 5 MINS • COOK TIME: 15 MINS • TOTAL TIME: 20 MINS 
              <br>
              <br> SERVES:4
              <BR>
              <br>
              <i> Super Easy One Pan Bourbon Chicken. Serve with rice and noodles to make it a meal!</i></p>

            <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2"><img src="http://everydaydishes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/easy-bourbon-chicken-everydaydishes_com-H.jpg" alt="..." class="img-fluid"></div>
